WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.862 --> 00:00:16.038
Swipe left to show the apps menu and tap "Camera"

00:00:16.038 --> 00:00:19.882
Tap the "Lens" icon

00:00:19.882 --> 00:00:25.916
Tap "find more lenses"

00:00:25.916 --> 00:00:29.647
Tap "Nokia Camera"

00:00:29.647 --> 00:00:32.217
Tap "install"

00:00:32.217 --> 00:00:34.841
Tap "allow"

00:00:39.810 --> 00:00:45.791
Swipe left to show the apps menu and tap "Settings"

00:00:45.791 --> 00:00:47.220
Swipe to applications tab

00:00:47.220 --> 00:00:51.929
Tap "photos + camera"

00:00:51.929 --> 00:00:55.348
Tap the box under "Pressing the camera button opens"

00:00:55.348 --> 00:00:57.704
Tap "Nokia Camera"

00:01:01.799 --> 00:01:13.220
Press the camera key to open Nokia Camera

00:01:13.220 --> 00:01:16.126
Tap the "Gallery" icon to enter photo gallery

00:01:16.126 --> 00:01:19.091
Slide to browse the photos

00:01:19.091 --> 00:01:22.990
Pinch to enter film view

00:01:22.990 --> 00:01:24.587
Tap the "Option" icon

00:01:24.587 --> 00:01:30.710
You may share, edit and delete the photo here

00:01:30.710 --> 00:01:35.471
Tap the "Arrow" icon to choose the camera mode

00:01:35.471 --> 00:01:40.872
Tap the "Camera Mode" icon

00:01:40.872 --> 00:01:44.127
The "Flashlight" icon is useless because lumia 525 don't have flash

00:01:44.127 --> 00:01:47.004
Tap the "Arrow" icon to adjust the camera settings

00:01:47.004 --> 00:01:50.729
Tap and slide the "Camera" icon to left, in order to open the settings menu

00:01:50.729 --> 00:01:57.749
Tap and drag the handle of "White Balance" to change the white balance

00:01:57.749 --> 00:02:06.734
Tap and drag the handle of "Focus" to change the focus

00:02:06.734 --> 00:02:20.091
Tap and drag the handle of "ISO" and "Shutter" to adjust the exposure manually

00:02:20.116 --> 00:02:27.369
Tap and drag the handle of "Exposure" to adjust the exposure

00:02:27.369 --> 00:02:31.861
Tap the "Camera" icon to shot photo

00:02:31.861 --> 00:02:34.255
Tap and slide the "Camera" icon to right to close the menu

00:02:34.255 --> 00:02:42.076
Tap the screen to focus

00:02:42.076 --> 00:02:54.669
Pinch or swipe up and down to zoom in/out

00:02:54.669 --> 00:03:12.863
Half press the camera key to focus, press and hold the camera key to do continuous shooting

00:03:12.863 --> 00:03:18.498
Tap and swipe down the "Camera" icon to "Camcorder" icon

00:03:18.498 --> 00:03:21.469
Tap the "Arrow" icon to show all the settings

00:03:21.469 --> 00:03:25.645
The "Video Light" icon is useless because lumia 525 don't have flash

00:03:25.645 --> 00:03:29.444
Tap and slide the "Camcorder" icon to left, in order to open the settings menu

00:03:29.444 --> 00:03:32.857
Tap and drag the handle of "White Balance" to change the white balance

00:03:32.857 --> 00:03:37.141
Tap and drag the handle of "Focus" to change the focus

00:03:37.141 --> 00:03:39.213
Tap and slide the "Camcorder" icon to right to close the menu

00:03:39.213 --> 00:03:42.790
Tap the "Camcorder" icon to start recording

00:03:42.790 --> 00:03:47.140
Swipe up or down to live zoom in/out

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:51.653
Cannot focus during recording

00:03:51.653 --> 00:03:53.778
Tap the "Camcorder" icon to stop recording

00:03:53.778 --> 00:04:01.620
Tap and swipe down the "Camcorder" icon to "Smart Sequence" icon

00:04:01.620 --> 00:04:04.022
Tap the focus point

00:04:04.022 --> 00:04:11.436
Tap the "Smart Sequence" icon to start taking photos

00:04:11.436 --> 00:04:16.013
Tap the "last taken photo" icon

00:04:16.013 --> 00:04:35.207
You may apply "Best Shot", "Action Shot", "Motion Focus", "Change Faces" and "Remove Moving Objects" effect to the photos

00:04:35.207 --> 00:04:43.778
Tap the "Options" icon

00:04:43.778 --> 00:04:49.529
Tap "settings"

00:04:49.529 --> 00:04:53.967
You may change "Framing grids", "Aspect ratio", "Face tracking", "Photo review" in pictures tab

00:04:53.967 --> 00:04:55.394
Slide to "Video" tab

00:04:55.394 --> 00:04:58.172
You may change "Framing grids", "Resolution", "Audio bass filter" in video tab

00:04:58.172 --> 00:05:00.268
Slide to "Smart Sequence" tab

00:05:00.268 --> 00:05:02.445
You may change "Photo review" here

